    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are robust: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Performance is further enhanced by a limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension geometry for precise turn-in. While it bears the honest patina of a driven machine, its powertrain remains tight and responsive, delivering that signature 8,000 RPM crescendo with absolute composure.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Engine runs smooth. Interior is clean with minor cosmetic wear. Maintenance records available. Reliable daily driver.",
