    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 530i in a sophisticated Alpine White finish. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. The exterior retains a deep gloss with only minor, age-appropriate road wear, while the Canberra Beige Dakota leather interior remains supple and smoke-free. Equipped with the Premium Package, you will enjoy heated front seats, a high-resolution navigation system, and a power tailgate. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the 2.0L turbocharged engine delivers smooth power, and the tires have significant tread remaining. Complete with two keys, all original manuals, and a comprehensive service log, this sedan is ready for its next owner who values both reliability and class.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
