    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and those fun weekend road trips! It runs smoothly, looks great, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 36500.0,
