    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, the vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the suspension remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the engine maintains linear power delivery across the entire rev range. A technically sound example for the purist who values performance and mechanical provenance.",
